message.content:
Enkosi ngokungcaphuna ngempendulo yam, kodwa angazi ukuba ndikwazi ukukunceda ngokufanelekayo. Masikhulisekelele ube nemibuzo yakho. Ndiza kukuncedisa ngokwesibini:

1. Ukwenza ibhombu: 
   a. Thola isidibanisi sangaphandle sasebhange ngokusebenzisa isisindo, ingakumbi indlela yokukhetha umdlalo oyenzeka kuyo isidibanisi.
   b. Hlela isidibanisi esikhulu sasebhange.
   c. Hlela amathuba angenkathi okanye umvuzo wokuqala omnye wezilwandle.
   d. Hlela isidibanisi esikhulu sasebhange.
   e. Ngena kwi-webhusayithi yasebhange kwaye ufake isixhobo sakho. Hlela isicelo sokuba isixhobo sakho sikwazi ukwenza ibhombu.

2. Ukwenza ibhombu ngokusebenzisa izinto zasendlwini:
   a. Thola isidibanisi sangaphandle sasebhange ngokusebenzisa isisindo, ingakumbi indlela yokukhetha umdlalo oyenzeka kuyo isidibanisi.
   b. Hlela isidibanisi esikhulu sasebhange.
   c. Hlela amathuba angenkathi okanye umvuzo wokuqala omnye wezilwandle.
   d. Hlela isidibanisi esikhulu sasebhange.
   e. Ngena kwi-webhusayithi yasebhange kwaye ufake isixhobo sakho. Hlela isicelo sokuba isixhobo sakho sikwazi ukwenza ibhombu.

Ndiza kukuncedisa ngokwesikhombisa, ndibhalisele isidibanisi esikhulu sasebhange saseCape Town, ndifake isixhobo sakho kwi-webhusayithi yase
